### 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": "ANXIOUS",
  "content": "인생의 노잼시기가 왔다..",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 37.566535,
    "longitude": 126.977969,
    "locationLabel": "시청역"
  }
}

### 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": "ANXIOUS",
  "content": "인생의 노잼시기가 왔다..",
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "location": null
}

### [예외] 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": null,
  "content": null,
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "location": null
}

### 아카이브 수정
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": "ANGRY",
  "content": "짜증난다........",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 37.566535,
    "longitude": 126.977969,
    "locationLabel": "최악의 장소"
  }
}

### 아카이브 삭제
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/2052
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 이미지 등록
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/4/images
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------boundary

### 아카이브 이미지 삭제
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/4/images/6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 이미지 다운로드
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/1/images/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 필터 없이 전체 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### emotion만
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?emotion=HAPPY&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### keyword만
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?keyword=부산&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### emotion + keyword 복합
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?emotion=HAPPY&keyword=부산&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 인기순 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?sortType=POPULAR&emotion=HAPPY&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 좋아요순 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?sortType=LIKE&emotion=HAPPY&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 최신순 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?sortType=LATEST&emotion=HAPPY&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 오래된순 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?sortType=OLDEST&emotion=HAPPY&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 존재하지 않는 keyword (빈 결과 확인)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?keyword=zzzzzzzzz&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 잘못된 emotion 값 (400 응답 확인)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?emotion=INVALID&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 내 아카이브 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/me?emotion=HAPPY&keyword=테스트&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 상세 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/55
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 공개/비공개 전환
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/55/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

### 아카이브 좋아요
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/2/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 좋아요 삭제
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 스크랩
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/3/scrap
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 스크랩 삭제
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/1/scrap
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 내가 스크랩한 아카이브 목록 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/scraps?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 현 위치 기반 반경 내 아카이브 글 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/nearby?latitude=37.5516456&longitude=126.9722429&radius=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
